Description:
Space and luxury !
Gary Joshi & Ray White proudly present this absolutely mesmerising ex-display/ sales office house in the ever popular Upper Point Cook Estate.
This spectacular east facing home embraces a modern feel with a succession of light filled living spaces. With superior fixtures and fittings all through and a great location, this home is the one you had been looking for all this long. The sustainable design of this home offers multiple living areas with a free flowing floor plan which is both practical and aesthetically appealing.
This fully upgraded Henley home features 4 bedrooms, a spacious theatre room , a study/home office , 2 bathrooms and 3 powder rooms, a retreat plus an alfresco.
The enormous master bedroom is befitting for a king and comes with 2 huge walk in robes and an enviable en-suite comprising of a double sized shower, double vanity and a bath tub.
2 of the remaining 3 bedrooms come with walk-in robes and the third has a spacious built in robe.All the bedrooms are very spacious and light filled and are facilitated by a huge centrally located bathroom that includes extended shower and bath tub with separate toilet powder room.
This house encompasses free flowing living and dining areas, incorporating a superb kitchen fitted with upgraded 900mm appliances, stone bench tops, and Island bench with breakfast bar, ample work space and storage including a butlers pantry.
With a mind boggling 57 squares(approx) of space on offer, this house is second to none when it comes to luxury and space . This magnificent property has the space , features and location et al that anyone has dreamt of owning in the suburb. This piece of art is waiting for the it's connoisseur to make it their own.
Other inspired features include :-
- East facing and park facing.
- Custom designed upgraded facade.
- Huge master bedroom befitting a king.
- Kitchen with a butlers pantry and bulk heads.
- High ceiling, down lights, timber floors to the living areas all aesthetically designed.
- Grand tiled alfresco sitting area with timber lined ceiling.
- Separate spacious dining area for the family to enjoy their meals.
- Walk in linen on both levels providing enough space for all your laundry needs.
- Oversized remote controlled garage with exposed concrete driveway.
- Fully landscaped front and backyards and fence all throughout the property with a side portico access.
- All this many many more .
With a park located right opposite the property , this house is perfectly suited for families with kids . Various reputed schools are in close proximity such as the Stella Maris catholic Primary school, Featherbrook P 9 and Point Cook P 9 college . The property is perfectly positioned between the point cook town centre and the featherbrook shopping centre to fulfill all the shopping needs.
The estate boasts of numerous parks, walking and cycling tracks which makes it the perfect estate for the family to live and enjoy.
Last but certainly not the least is the location which is right next to the freeway access, close to public transport and a short drive to the train station.
Perfectly priced, this beauty will not last long , so pick up the phone and Call Gary on 0410 947 568 to discuss further TODAY.

Description:
Luxurious Brand-New home in a Supreme Location
Reliance Real Estate proudly presents this gorgeously presented with all the major upgrades Prestigious Home in Albright estate with class throughout, perfect for those who won't compromise on quality and is sure to impress with its magnificent establishment's and list of luxurious appointments. Intelligent zoning and spacious lay out playing host to an open-plan living arrangement along with a highly functional modern and complete kitchen, boasting quality appliances, overlooking the light-filled living area; this residence is immediately inviting. With its striking street presence and free-flowing floor plan, this modern home dazzles from start to finish.
This remarkable house features: -
* Master Bedroom with double vanity en-suite and a massive walk- in robe.
* Three additional Bedrooms with mirrored built-in robes.
*Stunning tiled bathroom with freestanding bath-tub and extra-large shower
*900mm stainless steel upgraded appliances and quality dishwasher
*Large walk in pantry and tiled splashback
*High ceiling and high doors with solid front timber door
*Ducted heating and Evaporative cooling
*Alfresco for outdoor entertainment
*Timber flooring throughout; except wet areas
*Automatic double garage with remote control
*Fully Landscaped low maintenance front and back yard
This is a great opportunity to secure this beautiful home located in Albright estate one of Melbourne's most exciting and fastest growing areas, well-connected to everything you need and just 21kms from the CBD. With direct access to the West Gate Freeway it can be as fast as 30 minutes by car or take it easy and catch the train from Tarneit or the future station at Truganina.
There are plenty of schools in the area with a brand-new government primary school to be built right here in the community. The lively shopping centres and library in nearby Tarneit and Williams Landing are only a few minutes drive away and the planned Truganina local town centre located just over Dohertys Road.

Description:
2 KITCHENS, 3 LIVING ROOMS, 3 BEDROOMS!
Situated in a quiet Deer Park location, close to schools, parks, shops, public transport and freeway access, this neat and tidy home on a large 539m2 (approx.) parcel of land, is sure to suit first home buyers, investors and downsizers alike.
Comprising of three spacious bedrooms all with built in robes which are serviced by the bright central bathroom. The open plan living and meals area flow through to the kitchen featuring ample bench/storage space, oven and cooktop, adjacent to the second living space. At the rear of the home is a third living area with access from the back bedroom which includes a kitchenette and bathroom, set up perfectly for an under-roofline unit with external access (great potential to rent out) or for the growing family.
Moving outside this home further showcases a sunroom with access from the carport, creating the ideal space for a home office or gym! Further including extensive concreting, carport leading into a large pergola with access to the large shed and well maintained front & rear gardens. This gorgeous property also backs onto the Kororoit Creek Trail with easy access to the walking track and surrounding reserves and playgrounds!
Additional features include: heating, cooling, roller shutters, security doors, remote carport with drive through access and much more.
For all enquiries, call Shane Spiteri on 0488 980 115.

Description:
Suburban comfort and convenience
Inspection By Appointment Only.
Family comfort, phenomenal space and outstanding convenience this expansive property is designed to make you feel right at home the second you walk in the door.
A sought-after family focused location, residents are a stones throw away from Point Cook Coastal Park, Sanctuary Lakes Resort, Point Cook Shopping Centre and future Saltwater Coast Shopping Centre, a number of educational facilities, terrific parklands, cafes and restaurants, a number of public transport options incl. Williams Landing Train Station and easy access onto the freeway.
Downstairs Features:
- Generous open-plan living and dining area with polished timber floorboards, multiple windows that draw in abundant natural light and adjoining alfresco area - an ideal spot to relax or host guests.
- Effortlessly combining minimalism with functionality, the kitchen features a wide stone island bench/breakfast bar, ample storage space and high-quality stainless-steel appliances incl. a range-hood and dishwasher.
- Sizeable bedroom with built-in robe and en-suite.
- Power room.
- Storage room.
- Central air conditioning/heating.
- Double garage.
- Security alarm.
- Security doors.
Upstairs Features:
- Additional living area with adjoining balcony.
- Remaining 4 bedrooms with built-in robes. Master bedroom has access to a large walk-in robe and en-suite.
- Pristine central bathroom with mirrored vanity, shower, deep bathtub and toilet.
- Central air conditioning/heating.
Make the move and enjoy everything that this home has to offer.
Please contact Mo Mellak on 0405 083 188 to find out more and to arrange a viewing.

Description:
A recipe for success.
Perfectly positioned in a whisper-quiet street nearby the heart of Sunshine and parklands, this weather board home offers a great opportunity for home buyers or investors with future prospects on a large 585sqm approx. allotment.
Live in and enjoy the spacious three bedroom floorplan, serviced by a central bathroom, formal lounge and kitchen with meals area. With a wide drive and deep block, potential exists to re develop the entire site or possibly to the rear, subject to council approval.
A location prized for convenience, close to upcoming infrastructure projects including Sunshine Activity Hub (train and bus services), the 429 Bus, numerous schools plus ease of access to Hampshire Road Shopping/ restaurant district and to the CBD with a direct route via Wright Street. Families will also enjoy just a short stroll to the award winning Buckingham Reserve, Kororoit Creek trails and Arthur Beachley Reserve.

Description:
Effortless Living with Extensive Upgrades
LJ Hooker Point Cook presents 8 Saxby Street, Tarneit. Whether entertaining guests or spending time together as a family, this cool and contemporary residence delivers the perfect balance of space, lifestyle and convenience. Immaculately presented and comprising three living zones, four bedrooms, two bathrooms and double car accommodation, this is a property offers touches of luxe across its palatial proportions. Situated in a quiet and family-friendly neighbourhood, residents will enjoy proximity to local shops, schools and public transport.
- Abundant in light and space, this home offers three extensive living zones, including a formal lounge, open plan family and meals zone and an additional leisure room. The floorplan flows with ease across bright and breezy zones, with 2.7m ceilings and either timber laminate or glossy porcelain tiles underfoot.
- Relish effortless indoor / outdoor living with glass stacker doors leading to the covered alfresco. Following the main roof line, this tranquil space is finished with porcelain tiles, enjoying views across the lush, low maintenance lawn.
- The designer kitchen will delight the home chef, with gleaming 40mm stone countertops including a central island with breakfast bar, glossy cabinetry and a full-sized butlers pantry. Quality stainless-steel appliances include a Fisher and Paykel gas cooktop, under bench oven and canopy rangehood, alongside a Bosch dishwasher.
- Accommodation begins with the master suite, a heavenly haven and a true parents retreat, complete with walk-in-robe and luxurious en suite with stone countertops, dual vanity basins and an oversized shower. Three further bedrooms are offered, each spacious in size and with either built-in or walk-in robes, sharing access to the family bathroom with stone countertops, a tub and separate toilet.
- Additional appointments include a double remote-control garage with timber-look door and internal access, a large internal laundry with stone countertops and built-in cabinetry, walk-in linen closet, ducted heating, ducted cooling, timber laminate flooring, Colourbond fencing and quality roller blinds throughout.
With all amenities within easy reach, this location offers a lifestyle of quality and convenience. Local schools include Good New Lutheran P-12, The Grange P-12, Cambridge Primary School and the Islamic College of Melbourne, while local shopping precincts include Coles Tarneit West and Pacific Werribee. A plethora of playgrounds, reserves and walking tracks ensure that weekends are well spent, while commuters will benefit from nearby public transport options including both Tarneit and Hoppers Crossing stations.
Note. All stated dimensions are approximate only. Particulars given are for general information only and do not constitute any representation on the part of the vendor or agent.
